        <section id="dama-guide" class="pt-16 -mt-16 mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-700 mb-6 text-center">DAMA Skills Assessment Guide</h1>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <p class="mb-4 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    This section provides a step-by-step guide to applying for a DAMA Skills Assessment for various childcare occupations, based on information from ACECQA.
                </p>
                 <p class="mb-4 text-sm text-red-700 font-semibold">
                    **Important Note:** All applications must be submitted through ACECQA's online portal. Migration agents and applicants **MUST** use their own email addresses when registering for a new application.
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
                        <div class="accordion-header flex justify-between items-center" @click="open = !open">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600">Step 1 – Am I eligible for a DAMA skills assessment?</h2>
                            <span x-text="open ? '−' : '+'" class="text-2xl text-blue-600"></span>
                        </button>
                        <div x-show="open" x-cloak class="accordion-content mt-3 text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
                            <p>You are eligible to apply for an ACECQA DAMA skills assessment if your nominated occupation is Child Care Worker, Family Day Care Worker, Preschool Aide, or Out of School Hours Care Worker and you intend to migrate to Australia under a specified DAMA program.</p>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">Specific DAMA Programs by Occupation:</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                <li>
                                    <strong class="text-blue-700">Child Care Worker:</strong>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.ekcci.com.au/ek-dama/about-ek-dama/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline"> (East) Kimberley Region in Western Australia</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://www.cairnschamber.com.au/regional-migration/fnq-dama" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Far North Queensland</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://www.ckb.wa.gov.au/business-development/designated-area-migration-agreement/dama.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Goldfields Western Australia</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://gscdama.warrnambool.vic.gov.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Great South Coast region of Victoria</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://industry.nt.gov.au/migration-for-business/northern-territory-designated-area-migration-agreement" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Northern Territory</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="http://www.rdaorana.org.au/migration/dama/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Orana New South Wales</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://www.rdapilbara.org.au/dama" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Pilbara Region in Western Australia</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://migration.sa.gov.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">South Australia Regional</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://www.dardanup.wa.gov.au/our-shire/about-us/south-west-dama.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">South West Region of Western Australia</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://www.townsvilleenterprise.com.au/skills-and-migration/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Townsville</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong class="text-blue-700">Family Day Care Worker:</strong>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.ckb.wa.gov.au/business-development/designated-area-migration-agreement/dama.aspx" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Goldfields Western Australia</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                 <li>
                                    <strong class="text-blue-700">Preschool Aide:</strong>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.ekcci.com.au/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/Kimberley-DAMA-Occupation-List-public-version-v5.0.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">(East) Kimberley Region in Western Australia</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong class="text-blue-700">Out of School Hours Care Worker:</strong>
                                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.cairnschamber.com.au/regional-migration/fnq-dama" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Far North Queensland</a></li>
                                        <li><a href="https://www.rdapilbara.org.au/dama" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Pilbara Region in Western Australia</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mt-3">Before applying, ACECQA recommends you:</h3>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                <li>Check if your qualification appears on <a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/node/1090621/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">ACECQA's lists of approved qualifications</a>.</li>
                                <li>Check if the visa you intend to apply for requires a skills assessment.</li>
                                <li>Confirm which skilled occupation you require a skills assessment for.</li>
                                <li>Confirm you have sufficient post-qualification employment experience in the nominated occupation.</li>
                            </ul>
                             <p class="mt-2">You must check with the <a href="https://www.homeaffairs.gov.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Department of Home Affairs</a> before submitting your application to ensure your visa pathway requires a skills assessment.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
                        <div class="accordion-header flex justify-between items-center" @click="open = !open">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600">Step 2 - Read the DAMA Skills Assessment Application Guidelines</h2>
                            <span x-text="open ? '−' : '+'" class="text-2xl text-blue-600"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div x-show="open" x-cloak class="accordion-content mt-3 text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
                            <p>ACECQA assesses applications against the assessment standards set out in specific documents for each DAMA and occupation. Please refer to the links provided in Step 1 for your specific occupation and DAMA region, or the general <a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/31206" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">DAMA Skills Assessment Application Guidelines</a>.</p>
                            <p>If you are concerned that you may not satisfy these standards, you can seek general advice by calling <a href="tel:1300422327" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">1300 422 327</a> or emailing <a href="mailto:skilledmigration@acecqa.gov.au" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">skilledmigration@acecqa.gov.au</a>.</p>
                            <p>ACECQA cannot answer questions on migration, visa, or points requirements; direct these to the <a href="https://www.homeaffairs.gov.au/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Department of Home Affairs</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div x-data="{ open: false }" class="bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg shadow">
                        <div class="accordion-header flex justify-between items-center" @click="open = !open">
                            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-600">Step 3 - Prepare the required supporting documentation</h2>
                            <span x-text="open ? '−' : '+'" class="text-2xl text-blue-600"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div x-show="open" x-cloak class="accordion-content mt-3 text-neutral-700 space-y-2">
                            <p>The supporting evidence required depends on whether you already hold a suitable qualification or need NQF assessment.</p>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800">If you hold a suitable qualification:</h4>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                <li>Valid passport (identity/biometric pages)</li>
                                <li>Evidence of change of name (if applicable)</li>
                                <li>Evidence of ACECQA nationally approved certificate III (or higher) (if applicable)</li>
                                <li>Official certificate/parchment for your qualification(s)</li>
                                <li>Official academic transcript for your qualification(s) (all years of study)</li>
                                <li>Formal employment contract in the relevant occupation</li>
                                <li>Formal position description in the relevant occupation</li>
                                <li>Evidence of service registration/regulation for relevant employment</li>
                                <li><a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/41036" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Employer Reference Template</a> (completed by employer)</li>
                                <li><a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/41031" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Employment Experience Template</a> (completed by you)</li>
                                <li>Complete <a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/34851" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">DAMA Skills Assessment Applicant Declaration and Consent Form</a></li>
                                <li><a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/28601" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Authorised Representative Declaration and Consent Form</a> (if applicable)</li>
                                <li><a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/31711" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Migration Agent Declaration and Consent Form</a> (if applicable)</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h4 class="font-semibold text-neutral-800 mt-3">If you need NQF qualification assessment:</h4>
                             <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4">
                                <li><a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/28646" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Certified colour copies</a> of passport, change of name evidence, parchment, and academic transcripts</li>
                                <li>Evidence of <a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/41241" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">English language proficiency</a></li>
                                <li>Complete NQF Applicant Declaration and Consent Form (specific forms for <a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/28721" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Child Care/Family Day Care</a> or <a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/28731" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Outside School Hours Care</a>)</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p class="mt-2">Documents in languages other than English need formal translation (submit both original and certified translated copies).</p>
                            <p class="text-sm mt-2">Refer to <a href="https://www.acecqa.gov.au/media/31206" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">DAMA Skills Assessment Application Guidelines</a> for full details.</p>
                             <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-4 text-center">✨ Document Checklist Generator</h3>
                                <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-700">Generate a tailored checklist of documents required for your DAMA skills assessment.</p>
                                <div class="space-y-4">
                                    <div>
                                        <label for="docGenOccupation" class="block text-sm font-medium text-neutral-700 mb-1">Nominated Occupation:</label>
                                        <select id="docGenOccupation" class="w-full p-2 border border-neutral-300 rounded-md focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500">
                                            <option value="">Select Occupation</option>
                                            <option value="Child Care Worker">Child Care Worker</option>
                                            <option value="Family Day Care Worker">Family Day Care Worker</option>
                                            <option value="Out of School Hours Care Worker">Out of School Hours Care Worker</option>
                                            <option value="Preschool Aide">Preschool Aide</option>
                                        </select>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="flex items-center">
                                        <input type="checkbox" id="docGenNQFNeeded" class="h-4 w-4 text-blue-600 border-neutral-300 rounded focus:ring-blue-500">
                                        <label for="docGenNQFNeeded" class="ml-2 block text-sm text-neutral-900">I need my qualifications assessed under the NQF.</label>
                                    </div>
                                    <button id="generateDocChecklistBtn" class="w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-md hover:bg-blue-700 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-offset-2 transition duration-300">
                                        Generate Checklist
                                    </button>
                                    <div id="docChecklistLoading" class="text-center text-blue-600 mt-2 hidden">Generating checklist...</div>
