                                </div>
                            </div>
                             <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow">
                                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-700 mb-4 text-center">✨ English Language Proficiency Advisor</h3>
